DateTime::Locale::az_Cyrl(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::az_Cyrl(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::az_Cyrl

SYNOPSIS

  use DateTime;

  my $dt = DateTime->now( locale => 'az_Cyrl' );
  print $dt->month_name();

DESCRIPTION

This is the DateTime locale package for Azerbaijani Cyrillic.

DATA

This locale inherits from the DateTime::Locale::az locale.

It contains the following data.
